items.title: Astros win, magic number at 1
items.summary: After topping the Mariners, 8-6, on Saturday afternoon behind a pitching gem from Dallas Keuchel at Minute Maid Park, the Astros lowered their magic number to one for clinching their first division crown since moving to the American League West in 2013.
